OL,3,CWaste company fined after worker run
OL,4,Cover by excavator
OL,6,FA County Durham waste management
OL,7,Fcompany has been fined after an
OL,8,Femployee was run over by an excavator.
OL,10,FA 24-year-old man, who was in his
OL,11,Fsecond week of employment at Farm XS
OL,12,F(Northern) Limited in Barnard Castle,
OL,13,Fwas run over by the vehicle on 29
OL,14,FJanuary 2024, suffering fractures to
OL,15,Fboth feet.
