OL,4,Cover by excavator
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that the
OL,8,Fcompany had failed to ensure a safe
OL,9,Fsystem of work was in place. The HSE
OL,10,Fsays the man was working on a waste
OL,11,Fpile near moving vehicles with no
OL,12,Fphysical separation between them, and
OL,13,Fadded that there was no risk
OL,14,Fassessment or system of work to
OL,15,Fprotect pedestrians from vehicle
OL,16,Fmovements.
