OL,3,CWaste company fined after worker run
OL,4,Cover by excavator
OL,6,FAt Teesside Magistrates' Court on
OL,7,FTuesday 5 August, Farm XS (Northern)
OL,8,FLimited pleaded guilty to breaching
OL,9,Fthe Health and Safety at Work Act and
OL,10,Fwas fined #4,000, with a further
OL,11,F#4,285 to pay in costs.
OL,13,FGuidance states that pedestrians and
OL,14,Fvehicles should be segregated when
OL,15,Fwaste is being manually sorted. By
OL,16,Flaw, employers must ensure traffic
OL,17,Froutes can be used without risking the
OL,18,Fsafety of workers nearby.
