OL,6,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector
OL,7,FRichard McMullen said: "The outcome
OL,8,Fcould have been much worse. But the
OL,9,Ffailures that day meant a worker
OL,10,Freceived serious injuries.
OL,12,F"This should be a reminder to the
OL,13,Fwaste industry of the need to consider
OL,14,Fworkplace transport risks and to
OL,15,Fintroduce appropriate control measures
OL,16,Fto separate vehicles and pedestrians."
